nodejs
npm install -g create-react-app
npm create-react-app sampleproject

    OR

npx create-react-app myreactapp

4 phases
1.Mounting=>rendering the component
2.updating phase=>if any state change or prop change will occurs
3.unmounting=>remove component from the DOM
4.Exception handling

Mounting=>

- constructor()
  *static getDerivedStateFromProps()
  *render()
  \*componentDidMount()

to get the required dependencies
npm i @reduxjs/toolkit axios react-redux react-router-dom --save
